results.name: Decimal expansion of the sum of the reciprocals of A020330.
comment: The sum is 0.67014568628363761... . It can be computed relatively efficiently using a variation of the method of Joseph S. Myers (see link).
link: Joseph S. Myers, Palindome reciprocal sums [sic], SeqFan Mailing List, June 21, 2014.
